node.text: Was so lovely to meet @lailamuhammadtv from @nbc and tell them my story, how I started @nialayajewelry in a garage to opening a store on Melrose and what makes us so special ! I hope you’ll enjoy this. Happy Saturday 🌴🇺🇸 #nialaya #nbc #TV #californialive

node.text:
I did this fun TV show for Danish TV four years ago. It was a lot of fun as they followed me and my team
around, documenting how it is to live and do business in LA. Obviously very different from Denmark 🇩🇰 and then we always add a little “spice” to make it all a little more exciting. Lots of fun shooting it with very sweet people from Denmark and a lot of fun looking back at it too. Enjoy & Happy Thursday 🇺🇸🌴⚡️ #tbt #nialaya #tvshow #DanishTV

user.full_name: R I C A R D A 🌹

node.text: Everyday is international dog day for me. It's so beneficial to have a dog in your life. Obviously only dog owners understand what i'm talking about but that's ok too. Daisy is with me everyday at work and we are all so used to her being there than when she is at the groomer or home we miss her and think it's weird she isn't snoring in the background. Cheers to all dog owners around the world ❤️🐶
